# Resolved per machine on first `uv run`, not committed (repo-wide sidecar policy).
# The project env is dependency-free — serve.py is stdlib-only — and the TTS engine
# resolves in synth.py's own PEP 723 script env per platform: mlx-audio on Apple
# silicon (validated JCLAW-788); the NVIDIA/vLLM backend is deferred (JCLAW-788).
.venv/
uv.lock
__pycache__/
*.pyc
